OL,3,C'Devastating tragedy' as boy, 4,
OL,4,Cbecomes second life lost after house
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,FA four-year-old boy who was injured in
OL,8,Fa house fire in Wigan at the weekend
OL,9,Fhas now died, police said.
OL,11,FEthan Mason had been rescued after his
OL,12,F'dad ran back inside to save his
OL,13,Flittle boy', his family said.J.
OL,15,FEthan, who suffered serious injuries
OL,16,Fand was fighting for his life in an
OL,17,Finduced coma, died in hospital on
OL,18,FTuesday morning.
