OL,7,FDetective Inspector Lee Gridley, from
OL,8,FGMP's Wigan district, said: "This is a
OL,9,Fdevastating incident and all of our
OL,10,Fthoughts are with the family of this
OL,11,Fyoung boy, who had his entire life
OL,12,Fahead of him.
OL,14,F"Together with the earlier death, this
OL,15,Fis a tragedy for the Wigan community
OL,16,Fand I know that many people will be
OL,17,Fshocked by this heartbreaking news.
