OL,7,F"I hope people will join us in sending
OL,8,Ftheir absolute best wishes to all
OL,9,Fthose involved in this incident, as
OL,10,Fthey begin their journey in the
OL,11,Fhealing process. "
OL,13,FThe blaze broke out at around 2:30am
OL,14,Fon Sunday 14 April.
OL,16,FGreater Manchester Fire and Rescue
OL,17,Finvestigating the cause but, following
OL,18,Finitial enquiries, officers do not
OL,19,Fbelieve that there are any suspicious
OL,20,Fcircumstances.
